import './estilo.css';
import React from 'react';
import { Button, TextField, Box } from '@material-ui/core';



function DadosUsuario({aoEnviar}) {
    
    return (
        
        <form onSubmit={(event)=>{
            event.preventDefault();
            aoEnviar();
        }}>
            <TextField
                id="email"
                label="Email"
                type="email"
                variant="outlined"
                margin="normal"
                fullWidth
            />
            <TextField
                id="password"
                label="Senha"
                type="password"
                variant="outlined"
                margin="normal"
                fullWidth
            />
            <Box sx={{
                width: 500
            }}>
               <Button
                variant="contained"
                color="primary"
                type="submit">
                Voltar
            </Button>

            <Button
                variant="contained"
                color="primary"
                type="submit">
                Avan√ßar
            </Button> 
            </Box>
            
        </form>
    )
}

export default DadosUsuario
